title: Surface configuration of a safety cell for a vehicle

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a surface configuration of a safety cell for a vehicle, as shown and described.

description: This application is related to the following co-pending application, of the inventor, filed on even date herewith: application Ser. No. 29/267,009, entitled “Surface Configuration of a Vehicle, Toy, and/or Other Replicas”.
FIG. 1 is a side view of a first embodiment of a surface configuration of a safety cell for a vehicle according to my novel design;
FIG. 2 is a front perspective view thereof; and
FIG. 3 is a rear perspective view thereof.
FIG. 4 is a side view of a second embodiment of the surface configuration of a safety cell for a vehicle according to my novel design;
FIG. 5 is a front perspective view of FIG. 4; and,
FIG. 6 is a rear perspective view of FIG. 4.
